title: Dragon Wars - DVDRIP
description:
Meet Buraki, the vicious, 200-meter-long Imoogi serpent from ancient Korea. His army includes giant lizards with missile launchers, flying dragons, soldiers bred for evil and mega-intelligent dinosaurs. Together, they will destroy our cities unless reincarnated warriors 
Ethan and Sarah can outrun them and resurrect the good Imoogi, Buraki&#039;s ancient nemesis. Dragon Wars reveals every last detail of Earth&#039;s greatest battle-a war you&#039;ll only believe when you see it for yourself.

Approx. 90min
